      "text": "💾 存储：/data/reports/{model-id}.json + manifest.json\n\n🌐 前端：React 组件读取 JSON，支持模型视角切换\n   → 页面底部标注生成模型、时间、数据来源（透明化）\n   → 访问地址：luolei.org/about",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
